flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Monthly S&OP cycle initiation.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Initiate monthly S&OP cycle]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Data Quality & Validation - Perform data quality checks]
  N2 --> N3{PB: Cortex Auto Forecast - Select and deploy forecasting models}
  N3 -->|Primary| N4[Stream: STREAMS - Integrate data with ERP systems]
  N4 --> N5[PB: Process Builder - Develop technology roadmap]
  N5 --> N6[UI: Dimensions - Manage master data elements]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced COGS, amplified EBITDA, and unlocked working capital efficiency through improved data quality, integrated planning, and stable data flows.]
  N3 -->|Data quality issues detected| B1[Trigger data governance workflow]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Correct data quality issues before proceeding]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Forecast model accuracy below threshold| B2[Override with alternative model]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Improve forecast accuracy]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Integration failure| B3[Notify IT team for resolution]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Resume data flow and integration]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]